Package: sqlsauce
Title: The Secret Sauce for Dishing Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Bobby", "Fatemi", email = "bfatemi07@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains functionalities to simplify connections to a sql database,
    convenience wrappers around popular functions from the package RODBC, and
    utility functions that streamline the SQL to R workflow.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2)
Imports:
    stringr,
    gsubfn,
    RODBC,
    data.table,
    pryr,
    lazyeval,
    stringi
